{
  "stem": "23350.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the end, he gave me the certificate that I needed to be able to come to England.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was still lucky that in England, they didn't ask too many questions before I arrived.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because once I was there, they weren't going to send me back anywhere anymore.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But if they did find out before-- tuberculosis is a terrible thing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But thank goodness, what they did is, when I arrived, they took us to the-- to the doctor, you know, our whole group.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were being examined.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And when they saw that I had tuberculosis-- so they sent me to the-- to-- to-- to the sanatorium.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to Prague.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, no, we went.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We arrived in Prague.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in Prague, we were waiting months for the planes to arrive, for the RAF planes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we stayed in a hostel in-- it's like a hostel, like a Kinderheim, they called it-- a big house which they had taken over.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think that the American Joint paid for it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they paid, also, the-- the RAF to-- to bring us over, the American Joint.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the-- the RAF were the ones that brought us to-- to England.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were, in our transport, 300-- 300 or 320.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there are-- there were other transports who arrived later from different places.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we, from Theresien, arrived 320.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were only about 28 girls and the rest boys.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's why I'm one of the boys.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They call me one of the boys.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was fantastic.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The thing was that the planes were very small, because they were only bomber planes.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They put-- if they put 30 children into this plane, they were full.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one of the-- the pilots could see how cramped we are.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
